Documentation

type family Select (s :: Symbol) (ast :: a) = (v :: Type) Source #

Used to select a field type for a given AST.

Conventions for usage: If a selection is likely to be one of the "principal" newtypes (Expr, Pattern, etc), it should not be wrapped in ASTLocate, as this increases friction and creates redundant Located wrappers. This means that implementations should manually wrap in Locate if not using one of the principal newtypes
